name: Kevin Queen
bio: Husband to @queenrea & father to Raleigh, Camden, Durham, & Bolton. Lead Pastor @crosspoint.tv

social_posts.post_text: Congratulations @camden.queen on your acceptance to @samfordu @queenrea and I are so excited for you. They are getting beauty and strength, creative and compassion, an entrepreneurial spirit and a world changer. I believe these next four years are going to be amazing. We are so proud of you.

Today I had a really special Sunday. I had the honor of preaching an instillation service for one of my best friends in the world, Dustin Aagaard, as he became lead pastor at @fljourneychurch 

Dustin and I have been close friends for over 25 years. We first met at Atlanta Fest at Six Flags in 1994. (Scroll to see a photo of us swimming in the landscaped pool in front of Mind-bender) Another conversation for another day. 😉

Dustin is a great pastor and an even better friend. He has an incredible gift of encouragement, a passionate heart for God, and a humble others-focused life that inspires me. Journey, you’ve got a great one. @queenrea and I are so very excited and prayerfully expectant to see what the Lord has in store for @danish_pastor and @danish_pastors_wife

@camden.queen these four years of watching you cheer on the sidelines of gyms and fields have been so much fun. You’re amazing, you’ve worked so hard, brought all of who you are to the squad, and continue to show up as a leader. We love you and we’re so proud of you.
Happy Birthday @durham.queen we’re super proud of you. 16 years old! The year you’re officially taller than me (I concede) now and can pull off shorter shorts.
Happy Resurrection Day! My heart is full. So grateful for this fam and our @crosspoint.tv family and all that the Lord did this weekend. “He is risen, indeed!”
Happy Birthday Big ⚡️!!! 14! Love you buddy. So proud of you. To celebrate this day, as a bonus, I’ve included my favorite video of you dancing to the Spanish Alphabet.
Happy Mother’s Day @queenrea You were absolutely wonderful @crosspoint.tv today and for our family everyday. You hold it all together and make everything better. ❤️
Congratulations @camden.queen we’re so proud of you! ❤️ we had the most fun celebrating you. #samfordbound
Celebrating @camden.queen Happy 18! Love you so much Cam ♥️

11 years ago, @raleighqueenn and I went on a mission trip to Nicaragua when she was 8. It was an unforgettable experience. We’ve talked and dreamed about returning ever since. This week it became reality. We came back to Nicaragua with Amigos for Christ.

I’m beyond grateful for all that we experienced, from the beautiful families we were able to serve to the old friends we were able to see again. We’re headed home with full hearts. And as a dad, it doesn’t get any better than serving alongside Rals, seeing her compassion, love, fun, hard work, and heart to serve, the beautiful woman she has become. Until next time 🇳🇮.
We are so excited for @camden.queen starting at Samford. Such a special place to begin a new chapter. Huge piece of my heart in Birmingham. ❤️

This weekend was so very special for @queenrea and our family @crosspoint.tv having Pastor Kevin and Marcia Myers with us. Our 14 years @12stonechurch shaped us deeply, in our love for God, heart for people, and what faithfulness looks like in life and leadership. We’re beyond grateful for their lives and influence on us. Having PK up to preach at Cross Point was something we’ve talked and dreamed about for years. Yesterday, God fulfilled that dream and my heart is full.
Husband to @queenrea & father to Raleigh, Camden, Durham, & Bolton. Lead Pastor @crosspoint.tv
